reviews.text:
As per usual it can be oily but that's everywhere and considered normal--but if you're reading this likely you aren't fully aware of such a thing..

Food was good and the in-law come here on occasion as it's considered higher caliber.

Love this place.. perfect resto for big groups.. we like the Yummy legendary beijing roast pecking duck, crispy pork knuckle, nice corn soup, also the favourite one is beef and cabbage stir with sweet sauce..
Food quality is good. The venue is near and tidy. Peking duck is the signature dish.
We had really good service , food was great, 800 HKD for 5 people highly recommend
